{"tid":244207,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴力收廠】香港管不到內地業務 上市架構如虛設","createTime":"2017-05-15T08:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T05:16:17.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f25c78dc6f40274311f7970219b4e9313b6d4abf","tid":244207,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/165836_c2eb748a67a7875890336e21f3436aa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F165836_c2eb748a67a7875890336e21f3436aa4.jpg&h=708221af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州美亞獲廣東省工商局在2015年頒發「連續十年守信用重合同」獎狀。（張志華攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n美亞控股（1116）的股權糾紛，與之前爆發推土機大戰的山水水泥（691）股權鬧劇極為相似。在今年4月8日，山水水泥大股東天瑞集團意圖接管山水水泥濟南總部，以推土機強攻，千人打鬥，最後被當地公安驅趕。美亞控股和山水水泥均在港交所通告承認，已失去對內地經營實體公司的控制權。<br />\n<br />\n這兩家香港上市公司，亦早已罷免內地管理層的職務，但內地公司都是置之不理，而且還可以正常經營，與政府部門照打交道。記者在廣州美亞的會客室見到，公司獲得廣東省工商局在2015年頒發的「連續十年守信用重合同」獎狀，顯示內地官方部門並不理會與香港上市公司的糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n投資者學會主席譚紹興指，目前香港證監管不到內地，是上市制度的一個很大漏洞，建議投資者對這些存在股權糾紛的內地民企避之則吉。長遠而言，日後內地上市民企應該加大門檻，要求上市時出承諾函，避免香港控股公司管不到內地下屬公司的情況再出現。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃尹華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56689345&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56689345%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=f38570f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56689345%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=f5b14362\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56689345&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"0e4d4b9b4d30755981a294d225930d5d8873c8d3","tid":244207,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"【暴力收廠】美亞股權糾紛 過程複雜離奇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/170110_1fdca2b28018050f6c439d24a7f04d87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F170110_1fdca2b28018050f6c439d24a7f04d87.jpg&h=bddeef84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/170123_3fa48d541288e359d8d18b0b5aa8b483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F170123_3fa48d541288e359d8d18b0b5aa8b483.jpg&h=9cdf30d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/170135_0c70ee5f3814f845ba4b19bf0dc34edf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F170135_0c70ee5f3814f845ba4b19bf0dc34edf.jpg&h=aaddf079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美亞鋼管最早由羅氏家族在台灣創辦，在上世紀90年代擴展至廣州，並在2004年將廣州業務在香港上市，即美亞控股（1116），香港美亞上市公司持有廣州美亞84%股權，而台灣美亞則持有香港美亞上市公司21%股權，是當時最大股東。<br />\n<br />\n其後台資的美麗華集團獲羅氏家族引入，並派出蕭敏志和賴粵興任董事長和總經理，並託管台灣美亞所持的21%股權。但台灣美亞之後稱，香港美亞在2010年以6.2億元收購虛假的越南民進港項目，過程中台灣美亞所持有的21%香港美亞控股權被盜賣，股權離奇流失至兩家BVI（英屬處女群島）公司手上。本報在中央證券實物查冊，發現香港美亞上市公司股權分散，最大股東為兩家名為Bumper和Aspial的BVI公司，分別持17%和10%股權，最大的實名股東持股僅2%。<br />\n<br />\n因股權糾紛，香港美亞2012年起停牌，賴粵興在台灣被控告。2014年原董事會被罷免。在這5年期間，台灣美亞、香港美亞、賴粵興之間訴訟不斷。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃尹華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56689315&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56689315%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=cdc0b3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56689315%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=e2bc5716\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56689315&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"533627b937432866eb58ca4e3aad0867dec312aa","tid":244207,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb3cea6fb66d55622c95e0336698737859eb191","tid":244207,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港個幾條仚家剷咩來頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正一賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866c60789bed2821b32bb90d171ae6a0081a924a","tid":244207,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港個幾條仚家剷咩來頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正一賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個2條友反骨仔"}]}